2,"quote":{"pid":"95b89ba3d654bdea810e32e9996da53ccdca0bbe","tid":858372,"uid":97451,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"791e1c85d62854804f18ed3ea426848681ab1c7f","tid":858372,"uid":149494,"like":5,"dislike":52,"score":-47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T23:17:10.000Z","msg":"咁都睇唔明？文盲？<br />\n睇唔明又喊？做乜鳩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T00:22:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T00:24:49.000Z","msg":"我收到信之後哭了，因為看不懂<br />\n<br />\n果個咪你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4b257f67ad7d38061ae59d616c35bb5a6c5a9cb","tid":858372,"uid":64191,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T00:28:18.000Z","msg":"讓子彈飛係近年中國神作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca4b93082b9bed3117766d4086d01640a3554a63","tid":858372,"uid":130901,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"d4b257f67ad7d38061ae59d616c35bb5a6c5a9cb","tid":858372,"uid":64191,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T00:28:18.000Z","msg":"讓子彈飛係近年中國神作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T00:30:14.000Z","msg":"條女對奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb6e1de1e12bcef53b0bc779061c0cdde8f8fa65","tid":858372,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T00:30:52.000Z","msg":"基到 難怪發哥誤會"},{"pid":"c98478ed050a5466834cbff090319ad9f4d83353","tid":858372,"uid":174295,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T00:37:42.000Z","msg":"姜文啲戲真係好戲，讓子彈飛係中國特色嘅西部牛仔片，雖然讓子彈飛講嘅嘢其實係毛澤東思想（姜文係毛澤東fans），但係都不失為一部好戲<br />\n<br />\n其他啲戲都好睇，例如鬼子來了、陽光燦爛的日子"},{"pid":"591e2824c94d1bfcb417b5b6bf371a4f1dbcefca","tid":858372,"uid":3405,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T00:56:28.000Z","msg":"大哥 你是了解我的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f943e87b9dab28ebd61d4907eb17025e05175f20","tid":858372,"uid":3138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T01:27:21.000Z","msg":"同床嗰句係寫俾葛優封信到喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e728f98fc23cc4c2d8e17c657d31b9028c6dccde","tid":858372,"uid":137569,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7e8c9804d50eb82413ed12297dd326ebff89e117","tid":858372,"uid":42848,"like":102,"dislike":2,"score":100,"quote":{"pid":"b78d1a1da89c59e0e2507af24c4504017e6cf711","tid":858372,"uid":188176,"like":11,"dislike":8,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T23:26:05.000Z","msg":"其實寫得麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過姜文拍戲堅勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T23:42:53.000Z","msg":"葛優嗰封先係極品<br />\n<br />\n優優吾兄：<br />\n<br />\n壺口一別，竟有二七。春風秋月，楊柳依依。雖謀面不勤，卻心存惦記！吾兄凡新作問世，愚弟必爭先讀之。兄之身手爐火純青，每令愚弟嚎啕大悅。才驚四海，譽享中外。喜甚幸甚！<br />\n<br />\n新片籌備井然，故事隨信奉上。精華仍在提煉，腳本即將出膛。人物之妙，驚古爍今。且為兄之發揮，提供遼闊疆場。<br />\n<br />\n深信此角，必能助兄，繼往開來，再創輝煌。屆時億萬女粉，翻江倒海，拋家舍業，秋波明盪，不亦艷乎？<br />\n<br />\n縱使，狡兔八窟，數易家宅，亦難阻。擁躉之風暴，優黨之癡狂！直落得，隱身天涯，革面洗腸，不亦喜乎？<br />\n<br />\n吾兄片中雖無艷星共枕，但有愚弟陪床。醉眠秋共被，攜手日同行。耳鬢廝磨，卻非斷臂，不亦騷乎？<br />\n<br />\n新片除卻愚弟之外，尚有發哥亮相。左右拱衛，冬暖夏涼。不亦樂乎？<br />\n<br />\n喜騷艷樂，應有盡有，攬得雎鳩淑女，亮亮君子何求？聞聽吾兄將至，同仁上下，無不開顏。鬚眉腳撲朔，巾幗眼迷離。鼓瑟鼓簧為兄弟，磨刀霍霍向豬羊。<br />\n<br />\n呦呦鹿鳴，食野之蘋，悠悠我心，青青子衿。恰逢瑞雪早春，恕愚弟威逼利誘。皆因愛之心切，盼之心癢。江東渭北，春樹暮雲。書不盡言，晤面詳之。<br />\n<br />\n草此即問，全家均安。<br />\n<br />\n愚弟姜文"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T01:32:19.000Z","msg":"堆砌啫老實"},{"pid":"844c67633f2c01017683ae787f7d5a6de3628f90","tid":858372,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T01:32:24.000Z","msg":"用正體字定狗體字先?"},{"pid":"84c26d976ed3f8be201d3b5debdebe6fb3a0dd3c","tid":858372,"uid":35074,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T01:57:53.000Z","msg":"Kindest Regards <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明成封信都係中文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f4b019f50a87f7faec857f9f2e76fcb9d11375","tid":858372,"uid":144466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T01:59:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">發哥睇完仲喊，而且睇唔明</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3be7e1b4defc372a21c667f8b67b5a53df739ec3","tid":858372,"uid":67294,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0ceeedd7f3e81f8ee9e9f269ce8258e6eb2e838","tid":858372,"uid":55533,"like":114,"dislike":4,"score":110,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T23:11:37.000Z","msg":"雖然已經滲左少少共式中文<br />\n但篇文都算好文采<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T02:32:51.000Z","msg":"讓子彈飛係反共片黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"797358c2db354bf22af9b3d78e6695a4db3f1214","tid":858372,"uid":143399,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T02:33:54.000Z","msg":"吃一碗的粉 給一碗的錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e216ba6d11e8d94218c10457b873ab942e6b76b","tid":858372,"uid":206050,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3be7e1b4defc372a21c667f8b67b5a53df739ec3","tid":858372,"uid":67294,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0ceeedd7f3e81f8ee9e9f269ce8258e6eb2e838","tid":858372,"uid":55533,"like":114,"dislike":4,"score":110,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T23:11:37.000Z","msg":"雖然已經滲左少少共